<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | SchoolFlow</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1e3c72;
            --secondary: #2a5298;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-light: #64748b;
            --bg-body: #f8fafc;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            background: var(--bg-body);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* ---------- HEADER ---------- */
        .policy-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .policy-header h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .policy-header p {
            color: white;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* ---------- CONTENT ---------- */
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: -40px auto 80px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            transform: translateX(-5px);
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        h2 i {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        p,
        li {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .last-updated {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        /* ---------- RESPONSIVE ---------- */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin-top: 0;
                padding: 30px 20px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .policy-header {
                padding: 60px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include("partials/HomePageNavbar") %>

        <header class="policy-header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Your data security is our top priority at SchoolFlow.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="container">
            <a href="/" class="back-link"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home</a>

            <span class="last-updated">Last Updated: May 2024</span>

            <p>Welcome to <strong>SchoolFlow</strong>. We value the trust you place in us when sharing school data. This
                policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i> 1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect information necessary to provide seamless school management services:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>School Data:</strong> Name, address, and contact details of the institution.</li>
                <li><strong>Student & Parent Data:</strong> Names, enrollment numbers, attendance records, and contact
                    information.</li>
                <li><strong>Financial Data:</strong> Fee payment history and transaction IDs (processed securely via
                    Razorpay).</li>
            </ul>

            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-check"></i> 2. How We Use Data</h2>
            <p>Your data is used strictly for school-related operations:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To manage attendance and academic results.</li>
                <li>To facilitate online fee payments and generate receipts.</li>
                <li>To send important announcements and notifications via the portal.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user-secret"></i> 3. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement industry-standard encryption to protect your data. We do not sell or rent your personal
                information to third-party advertisers. Access to data is restricted to authorized school administrators
                and teachers only.</p>

            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i> 4. Payment Information</h2>
            <p>All payments are processed through <strong>Razorpay</strong>. SchoolFlow does not store your credit card
                or bank login details on our servers. Please refer to Razorpay’s Privacy Policy for more details on
                payment security.</p>

            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> 5. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or data protection, please reach out to our
                support team at:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@schoolflow.com</p>
        </div>

        <%- include("partials/HomePageFooter") %>
            <%- include("../partials/app-back-handler") %>
</body>

</html>